(2, 1, '2015-09-10 18:43:34', '2015-09-10 18:43:34', 'This is an example page. It''s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\r\n<blockquote>Hi there! I''m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin'' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\r\n...or something like this:\r\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\r\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-admin/">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!', 'News', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'news', '', '', '2015-12-07 20:39:00', '2015-12-07 20:39:00', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(5, 1, '2015-09-10 20:23:26', '2015-09-10 20:23:26', '[su_row class="hero-banner"]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="3/4" class="image"]\r\n<h4>We’re a high octane agency based in Houston, Texas… Driven by results and powered by caffeine. Grab a cup, sit back and see what we can do.</h4>\r\n[/su_column] [su_column size="1/4" class="text"]\r\n<h2>IT’S ALL IN THE PROCESS</h2>\r\nIt’s no coincidence that we’re one of the top agencies in Texas. Our proven Clarify, Brand, Reach process builds awareness and generates traffic. Whether you’re a major real estate development or an organic baby product we’ve got the process that will help you succeed.\r\n<ul class="icons">\r\n	<li><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-228" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/icon_clarify.png" alt="icon_clarify" width="60" height="60" />\r\nClarify</li>\r\n	<li><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-227" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/icon_brand.png" alt="icon_brand" width="60" height="60" />\r\nBrand</li>\r\n	<li><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-226" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/icon_reach.png" alt="icon_reach" width="60" height="60" />\r\nReach</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Capabilities Include</h3>\r\n<h5>(but are not limited to):</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Consulting and Market Research</li>\r\n	<li>Concept and Creative Strategy and Development</li>\r\n	<li>Print and Digital Graphic Design</li>\r\n	<li>Broadcast Creative and Production</li>\r\n	<li>Media Strategy, Planning and Buying</li>\r\n	<li>Full Digital Media Capabilities</li>\r\n	<li>Tracking, Reporting and Reconciliation</li>\r\n	<li>Social Media, Public Relations and Event Planning</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[/su_row]\r\n\r\n[su_row class="news"]\r\n\r\n[frontpage_news widget="25" name="News"]\r\n\r\n[/su_row]\r\n\r\n[su_row class="thoughts"]\r\n\r\n[frontpage_news widget="44" name="Thoughts"]\r\n\r\n[/su_row]\r\n\r\n[su_ro