(455, 1, '2015-11-23 18:16:39', '2015-11-23 18:16:39', '<h1><img class="size-full wp-image-614 alignleft" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/coffee.png" alt="coffee" width="386" height="386" /></h1>\r\nAtlantic Coffee Solutions recognized our passion for coffee and solid marketing strategies when they chose Manlove to brand their state-of-the-art decaffeination process. ACS, one of the largest coffee manufacturers in the world, utilizes the supercritical carbon dioxide and ultra-pure water process for a decaffeinated product like no other. It’s effective, completely natural, chemical free and and a precise process of removing caffeine in the shortest amount of time, leaving all flavor and aroma components intact.\r\n\r\nEven the caffeine fans at Manlove can’t deny this is one good cup of java.\r\n\r\nUPDATE: Manlove has completed the Clarify step of our own process with some solid market research and brand positioning. Stay tuned as we move into the Brand stage. We’re excited to launch the new creative in the first quarter of 2016.', 'We Know Joe!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'we-know-joe', '', '', '2015-11-30 19:32:14', '2015-11-30 19:32:14', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/?p=455', 0, 'post', '', 0),
