(494, 1, '2015-11-23 19:58:24', '2015-11-23 19:58:24', '[su_row class="about-us"]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/2"]\r\n<h1>About Us</h1>\r\n<blockquote>“A campaign should take you somewhere new, someplace you haven’t been before – that is our measure of success.”</blockquote>\r\n<img class="size-full wp-image-344 alignright" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/jmmc_sig_black.png" alt="jmmc_sig_black" width="250" height="49" />\r\n\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/2"]\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-350" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/placeholder_window.jpg" alt="placeholder_window" width="600" height="596" />\r\n\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[/su_row]\r\n\r\n[su_row class="years"]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/2"]\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-355" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/about_press.jpg" alt="about_press" width="600" height="521" />\r\n\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/2"]\r\n<h2>50 years dreaming</h2>\r\n50 years ago, an ambitious young man had a vision to create measurable results for all of his clIents, a strategy that has served his company well. Starting with a one-color printing press in his father’s garage, John Manlove set out on a journey to create one of the largest, most award winning agencies in the Houston area.\r\n\r\nThe experience of building a business from the ground up and helping many companies build theirs, has left a permanent value system within John Manlove Marketing &amp; Communications. Values that include: give the client more than they expect, create campaigns based on proven fundamentals, and build the company on lasting relationships.\r\n\r\nJohn Manlove Marketing &amp; Communications is a company with decades of experience and the kind of knowledge you want on your team. Whether B2B or B2C we have improved the effectiveness of every campaign we have been involved with. John Manlove Marketing &amp; Communications is a company that has a history of creating results.\r\n\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[/su_row]\r\n\r\n[su_row class="john featured"]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/2"]\r\n<h2>John Manlove</h2>\r\n<p class="p1">John Manlove, 62 years old, was raised in the advertising industry. He has built his business from a one-car garage into one of the largest most successful marketing and communication firms in the Houston area. Started in 1961 his agency is the oldest and one of the most respected firms in the Houston area. John also built and sold two companies, a printing company and ChurchMarketing.com. John Manlove also created two startup companies, ITZ Floral in 2006 which imported pre-packaged flowers direct from Guatemala to Houston and a specialty coffee company started in 2012.</p>\r\n281 234 5678\r\n<a href="mailto:john@johnmanlove.com">john@johnmanlove.com</a>\r\n\r\nSocial Media\r\n\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/2"]\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-360" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/placeholder_john.jpg" alt="placeholder_john" width="600" height="599" />\r\n\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[/su_row]\r\n\r\n[su_row class="gina featured"]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/2"]\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-363" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/placeholder_gina.jpg" alt="placeholder_gina" width="600" height="600" />\r\n\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/2"]\r\n<h2>Gina Manlove</h2>\r\n<p class="p1">Gina joined the agency in 1997 and leads the day-to-day activities of the agency as well as managing her own client base. She has been the lead senior account manager for Shell managing all aspects of the account for nine years, planned strategy and media placement for the Grand Opening of HCA Heart Hospital, managed all aspects of producing three hard bound books – projects total $450k and other clients. The Woodlands CVB was recipient of her management skills and for seven years she successfully planned the marketing budget, creative, events while exceeding goals year after year. She is currently the senior account manager for Toll Brothers first master planned community in the country, Woodson’s Reserve. She has just completed the 2016 Strategic plan – complete with budget/media allocations, Grand Opening, 24 events and a Realtor program launch.</p>\r\n281 234 5678\r\n<a href="mailto:gina@johnmanlove.com">gina@johnmanlove.com</a>\r\n\r\nSocial Media\r\n\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[/su_row]\r\n\r\n[su_row class="team"]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/3 leah"]\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-366" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/placeholder_employee.jpg" alt="placeholder_employee" width="400" height="400" />\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Leah Howard</h3>\r\n<h5>Vice President &amp; Brand Development Director</h5>\r\n<p class="p1">Leah Manlove Howard grew up in the marketing business as third generation. She now uses that expertise when planning and strategizing for clients. As Vice President and Brand Development Director, she develops a client’s brand, marketing strategy and assures that each campaign is on message and effectively reaches its goals. During her time at Manlove, she has also helped launch many of the company’s internal ventures, including a magazine and an international flower delivery company. Leah has a Bachelor’s of Business Administration in Marketing from Baylor University.</p>\r\n<a href="mailto:lmhoward@johnmanlove.com">lmhoward@johnmanlove.com</a>\r\n\r\nSocial Media\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/3 mel"]\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-366" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/placeholder_employee.jpg" alt="placeholder_employee" width="400" height="400" />\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Melody Farkas</h3>\r\n<h5>Chief Operating Officer</h5>\r\n<p class="p1">Melody Manlove Farkas also grew up in marketing, but she primarily applies her experience to production and project management. Her vast knowledge of production time lines and vendor relations help ensure quality products are delivered on time each time, and at a reasonable cost. She has a Bachelor’s of Arts in Communications from Baylor University.</p>\r\n<p class="p1"><a href="mailto:mmfarkas@johnmanlove.com">mmfarkas@johnmanlove.com</a></p>\r\nSocial Media\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/3 eddy"]\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-366" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/placeholder_employee.jpg" alt="placeholder_employee" width="400" height="400" />\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Eddy Henry</h3>\r\n<h5>Chief Creative Officer</h5>\r\n<p class="p1">With 30 years of experience in marketing and advertising Eddy has created, designed, art directed and produced campaigns across all forms of media. He has worked for a wide variety of industries including travel and tourism, real estate, home renovation and repair, fashion, energy, automotive, financial and more. His innovative approach to developing creative and a top-notch creative staff have helped position John Manlove Marketing &amp; Communications as one of the top creative firms in the southwest. Eddy strives to produce creative that speaks to the audience whether using humor, attitude, or straight forward information, and takes great pride in the ROI his work has brought to our clients. Eddy has a Bachelor’s of Science in Journalism from Texas A&amp;M University - Commerce.</p>\r\n<a href="mailto:ehenry@johnmanlove.com">ehenry@johnmanlove.com</a>\r\n\r\nSocial Media\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[/su_row]\r\n\r\n[su_row class="our-team"]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/1"]\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-283" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/icon_title-spheres.png" alt="icon_title-spheres" width="40" height="40" />\r\n<h2>Our Team</h2>\r\nManlo