anagement skills and for seven years she successfully planned the marketing budget, creative, events while exceeding goals year after year. She is currently the senior account manager for Toll Brothers first master planned community in the country, Woodson’s Reserve. She has just completed the 2016 Strategic plan – complete with budget/media allocations, Grand Opening, 24 events and a Realtor program launch.</p>\r\n281 234 5678\r\n<a href="mailto:gina@johnmanlove.com">gina@johnmanlove.com</a>\r\n\r\nSocial Media\r\n\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[/su_row]\r\n\r\n[su_row class="team"]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/3 leah"]\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-498" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/leah.jpg" alt="leah" width="600" height="600" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Leah Howard</h3>\r\n<h5>Vice President &amp; Brand Development Director</h5>\r\n<p class="p1">Leah Manlove Howard grew up in the marketing business as third generation. She now uses that expertise when planning and strategizing for clients. As Vice President and Brand Development Director, she develops a client’s brand, marketing strategy and assures that each campaign is on message and effectively reaches its goals. During her time at Manlove, she has also helped launch many of the company’s internal ventures, including a magazine and an international flower delivery company. Leah has a Bachelor’s of Business Administration in Marketing from Baylor University.</p>\r\n<a href="mailto:lmhoward@johnmanlove.com">lmhoward@johnmanlove.com</a>\r\n\r\nSocial Media\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/3 mel"]\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-366" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/placeholder_employee.jpg" alt="placeholder_employee" width="400" height="400" />\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Melody Farkas</h3>\r\n<h5>Chief Operating Officer</h5>\r\n<p class="p1">Melody Manlove Farkas also grew up in marketing, but she primarily applies her experience to production and project management. Her vast knowledge of production time lines and vendor relations help ensure quality products are delivered on time each time, and at a reasonable cost. She has a Bachelor’s of Arts in Communications from Baylor University.</p>\r\n<p class="p1"><a href="mailto:mmfarkas@johnmanlove.com">mmfarkas@johnmanlove.com</a></p>\r\nSocial Media\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/3 eddy"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Eddy Henry</h3>\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-499" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/eddy.jpg" alt="eddy" width="600" height="600" />\r\n<h5>Chief Creative Officer</h5>\r\n<p class="p1">With 30 years of experience in marketing and advertising Eddy has created, designed, art directed and produced campaigns across all forms of media. He has worked for a wide variety of industries including travel and tourism, real estate, home renovation and repair, fashion, energy, automotive, financial and more. His innovative approach to developing creative and a top-notch creative staff have helped position John Manlove Marketing &amp; Communications as one of the top creative firms in the southwest. Eddy strives to produce creative that speaks to the audience whether using humor, attitude, or straight forward information, and takes great pride in the ROI his work has brought to our clients. Eddy has a Bachelor’s of Science in Journalism from Texas A&amp;M University - Commerce.</p>\r\n<a href="mailto:ehenry@johnmanlove.com">ehenry@johnmanlove.com</a>\r\n\r\nSocial Media\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[/su_row]\r\n\r\n[su_row class="our-team"]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/1"]\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-283" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/icon_title-spheres.png" alt="icon_title-spheres" width="40" height="40" />\r\n<h2>Our Team</h2>\r\nManlove has scoured the best coffee shops in the world to find the most creative and dedicated marketing experts in the world. From the Champs Elysées of Paris, to the Salsa music capital of the world Cali, Colombia, to the streets of Houston we have built a remarkable team of branding professionals.\r\n\r\nOur international staff creates unforgettable campaigns that generate results, garnish awards, and build awareness for a diverse group of clients. To know our team is to know the best in the industry.\r\n\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[/su_row]\r\n\r\n[su_row class="team"]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/3 vicente"]\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-366" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/placeholder_employee.jpg" alt="placeholder_employee" width="400" height="400" />\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Vicente Yuste</h3>\r\n<h5>Art Director</h5>\r\n<p class="p1">Originally from Madrid, Spain, Vicente Yuste has over 15 years of experience working with international clients as a Graphic Designer and Art Director. Winning awards from prestigious associations like the American Advertising Federation and being published in respected design publications such as... LogoLounge and BranD Magazine is routine for Vicente. At JMMC, he has been a vital part of our corporate rebranding and revitalizing new and existing clients’ marketing campaigns. Vicente has worked with clients like Wal-Mart, Guinness, Heineken, MaxFactor, and Cadbury-Schweppes.</p>\r\n<a href="mailto:vicente@johnmanlove.com">vicente@johnmanlove.com</a>\r\n\r\nSocial Media\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/3 rick"]\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-366" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/placeholder_employee.jpg" alt="placeholder_employee" width="400" height="400" />\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Rick Celeita</h3>\r\n<h5>Lead Web Developer</h5>\r\n<p class="p1">With over 10 years of experience, Rick Celeita has been at the cutting edge of web trends and technologies since graduating with honors from The Art Institute of Houston in 2005. As Lead Web Developer, Rick is involved in all interactive projects - from inception to launch - to ensure that they not only look good, but that the code that makes them work is clean and up to the latest web standards. He has worked with clients such as HBO, Paramount Pictures, Mattel, The Department of Veterans Affairs - Palo Alto, The University of Texas Medical Branch, and The Hanover Company.</p>\r\n<a href="mailto:rick@johnmanlove.com">rick@johnmanlove.com</a>\r\n\r\nSocial Media\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/3 amber"]\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-366" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/placeholder_employee.jpg" alt="placeholder_employee" width="400" height="400" />\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Amber Ebrahim</h3>\r\n<h5>Graphic Designer</h5>\r\n<p class="p1">Amber is a highly creative and multitalented Graphic Designer with experience in multimedia, marketing, and print design. She is passionate and an inventive creator of innovative marketing strategies and campaigns, all while performing in deadline-driven environments with an emphasis on working within budget requirements.</p>\r\n<a href="mailto:amber@johnmanlove.com">amber@johnmanlove.com</a>\r\n\r\nSocial Media\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[/su_row]\r\n\r\n[su_row class="awards"]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/4"]\r\n<h2>Awards</h2>\r\nWe’ve been recognized by some of the finest organizations in the world\r\n\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/4"]\r\n<h3>Addy   <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-369" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/bgd_addy.png" alt="bgd_addy" width="57" height="81" /></h3>\r\nSed ut perspiciatis unde omnis iste natus error sit voluptatem accusantium doloremque laudantium, totam rem aperiam, eaque ipsa quae ab illo inventore veritatis et quasi architecto beatae vitae dicta sunt explicabo.\r\n\r\n<span style="color: