(507, 1, '2015-11-23 22:13:38', '2015-11-23 22:13:38', '[su_row class="hero-banner"]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="3/4" class="image"]\r\n<h4>We’re a high octane agency based in Houston, Texas… Driven by results and powered by caffeine. Grab a cup, sit back and see what we can do.</h4>\r\n<p class="signature"><img class="size-full wp-image-207 alignright" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/john_signature.png" alt="john_signature" width="123" height="24" /></p>\r\n[/su_column] [su_column size="1/4" class="text"]\r\n<h2>IT’S ALL IN THE PROCESS</h2>\r\nIt’s no coincidence that we’re one of the top agencies in Texas. Our proven Clarify, Brand, Reach process builds awareness and generates traffic. Whether you’re a major real estate development or an organic baby product we’ve got the process that will help you succeed.\r\n<ul class="icons">\r\n	<li><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-228" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/icon_clarify.png" alt="icon_clarify" width="60" height="60" />\r\nClarify</li>\r\n	<li><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-227" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/icon_brand.png" alt="icon_brand" width="60" height="60" />\r\nBrand</li>\r\n	<li><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-226" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/icon_reach.png" alt="icon_reach" width="60" height="60" />\r\nReach</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Capabilities Include</h3>\r\n<h5>(but are not limited to):</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Consulting and Market Research</li>\r\n	<li>Concept and Creative Strategy and Development</li>\r\n	<li>Print and Digital Graphic Design</li>\r\n	<li>Broadcast Creative and Production</li>\r\n	<li>Media Strategy, Planning and Buying</li>\r\n	<li>Full Digital Media Capabilities</li>\r\n	<li>Tracking, Reporting and Reconciliation</li>\r\n	<li>Social Media, Public Relations and Event Planning</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[/su_row]\r\n\r\n[su_row class="news"]\r\n\r\n[frontpage_news widget="25" name="News"]\r\n\r\n[/su_row]\r\n\r\n[su_row class="thoughts"]\r\n\r\n[frontpage_news widget="44" name="Thoughts"]\r\n\r\n[/su_row]\r\n\r\n[su_row class="home-video"]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="3/4" class="video"]\r\n\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2hBAPrwYINo\r\n\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/4" class="video-text"]\r\n<h3>"We''ve Arrived" - JMMC TV Campaign Wins Big</h3>\r\nJMMC is launching 2015 with a new ad campaign for Bridgeland featuring a television spot filmed by Director Kerry Shaw Brown. The theme We’ve Arrived will be utilized across several platforms including print, broadcast, outdoor and web/interactive. Watch the spot and see how JMMC brings to Life Well Played.\r\n\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[/su_row]\r\n\r\n[su_row class="fields"]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/4" class="retail"]\r\n\r\n<a href="#">Retail</a>\r\n\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/4" class="real-estate"]\r\n\r\n<a>Real Estate</a>\r\n\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/4" class="beverages"]\r\n\r\n<a>Beverages &amp; Food</a>\r\n\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/4" class="energy"]\r\n\r\n<a>Energy</a>\r\n\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[/su_row]\r\n\r\n[su_row class="social"]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/2" class="youtube"]\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<img src="/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/icon_yt.png" alt="YouTube Icon" />\r\n<h2>JMMC_Talks</h2>\r\n<a href="https://youtu.be/-PT9lWe08XI">subscribe</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/4" class="instagram"]\r\n[instagram-feed]\r\n<div class="insta-div">\r\n\r\n<img src="/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/icon_instagram.png" alt="Instagram Icon" />\r\n<h2>#jmmc_agency</h2>\r\n<a href="https://www.instagram.com/jmmc_agency/">follow</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/4" class="facebook"]\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<img src="/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/icon_fb.png" alt="Facebook Icon" />\r\n<h2>