 successfully planned the marketing budget, creative, events while exceeding goals year after year. She is currently the senior account manager for Toll Brothers first master planned community in the country, Woodson’s Reserve. She has just completed the 2016 Strategic plan – complete with budget/media allocations, Grand Opening, 24 events and a Realtor program launch.</p>\r\n281 234 5678\r\n<a href="mailto:gina@johnmanlove.com">gina@johnmanlove.com</a>\r\n\r\nSocial Media\r\n\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[/su_row]\r\n\r\n[su_row class="team"]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/3 leah"]\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-498" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/leah.jpg" alt="leah" width="600" height="600" />\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Leah Howard</h3>\r\n<h4>Vice President/\r\nBrand Development Director</h4>\r\n<p class="p1"><a href="mailto:lmhoward@johnmanlove.com">lmhoward@johnmanlove.com</a></p>\r\nSocial Media\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/3 mel"]\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-366" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/placeholder_employee.jpg" alt="placeholder_employee" width="400" height="400" />\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Melody Farkas</h3>\r\n<h4>Chief Operating Officer</h4>\r\n<p class="p1"><a href="mailto:mmfarkas@johnmanlove.com">mmfarkas@johnmanlove.com</a></p>\r\nSocial Media\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/3 madison"]\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-499" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/eddy.jpg" alt="eddy" width="600" height="600" />\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Madison Henry</h3>\r\n<h4>Account Planner</h4>\r\n<p class="p1"><a href="mailto:madison@johnmanlove.com">madison@johnmanlove.com</a></p>\r\nSocial Media\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[/su_row]\r\n\r\n[su_row class="our-team"]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="2/3"]\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-283" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Co