rint, visual, audio and web materials and programs. The MarCom statuette graces the trophy cases of some of the top business and communication firms in the world. </span></p>\r\n<span style="color: #e64d61;">16 Gold </span>\r\n<span style="color: #e64d61;">10 Silver </span>\r\n<span style="color: #e64d61;">10 Excellences</span>\r\n\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/4"]\r\n<h3>Davey   <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-688" src="http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/davey_awards_gold.jpg" alt="davey_awards_gold" width="31" height="81" /></h3>\r\n<p class="p1">The Davey Awards honors the best in Web, Design, Video, Advertising, Mobile &amp; Social from small agencies worldwide.</p>\r\n<p class="p1"><span style="color: #e64d61;">16 Gold </span>\r\n<span style="color: #e64d61;">10 Silver </span>\r\n<span style="color: #e64d61;">10 Excellences</span></p>\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[/su_row]\r\n\r\n[su_row class="video"]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="1/1"]\r\n\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/embed/-PT9lWe08XI\r\n\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[/su_row]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '150-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-03 21:06:42', '2015-12-03 21:06:42', '', 150, 'http://localhost:8888/JMMC_Corp-Site/150-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
